(1, 'CBD Boxes', 'cbd-boxes', 'Implementing the right packaging solution is an important part of your CBD product marketing strategy. CustomBoxesUS, a great source for CBD boxes, can bring innovations to your brand and create a distinct look that you need to increase sales. Make the right impression with your customers by delivering promised quality and effectiveness. Contact us!', '<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We at CustomBoxesUs pride ourselves on\r\nproviding the best custom packaging boxes and services in the industry. There\r\nare no other manufacturers that can match our quality products, an extensive\r\nselection of sizes, and personal attention to detail. We work hard to provide you\r\nwith a high-quality product at a great price! If you\'re looking for a reliable\r\ncompany that is dedicated to bringing you the best custom packaging solutions\r\navailable anywhere then you\'ve come to the right place!</span><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26);\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', 'cbd-boxes.png', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Custom CBD BOXES: A unique way\r\nto make your cannabis products appealing:<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">Custom CBD boxes are the ideal\r\npackaging for your products. They come in handy when you want to carry a lot of\r\nstuff with you. And they can also be applicable as gift boxes due to their\r\nattractive appearance and style. We produce custom CBD boxes in different\r\nshapes and sizes. Our creators have been working on custom designs according to\r\nour customers’ needs and requirements in order to serve them better. We offer\r\nfree delivery services as well, so buyers need not worry about any charges or\r\nextra taxes because we will bear all of them.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Our customization services\r\ninclude:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Raw Material<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Sizes and Shapes (varies on the product you deal with)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Custom Designs<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Raw Material:<o:p></o:p></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">You can get your custom CBD boxes\r\ntailor-made of kraft paper, cardboard, and corrugated material. When you are\r\ngoing to choose the material, you need to keep in mind the texture. Kraft paper\r\nwill give you an elegant and classic sense. Instead, corrugated material is\r\nmore durable than kraft paper.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">If the product is not too sensitive\r\nto touch, then cardboard will be a perfect choice as well as they are more\r\ncost-effective than other materials. The price of cardboard varies according to\r\nits quality and grade.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Sizes and Shapes:<o:p></o:p></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">We can customize your sizes and\r\nshapes as per your product requirements. A custom-made product will increase\r\nthe value of your brand. If you choose a small design, you can get it in a\r\nsmall box. On the other hand, if you are looking for something larger and more\r\nappealing to look at, then the bigger boxes will give you a greater appeal.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Custom Designs:<o:p></o:p></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">We provide free design services as\r\nwell. You can leave any kind of message or logo on your custom-made CBD boxes.\r\nThe design and choice of colors will depend on your product, yet one thing is\r\ncertain they definitely should be catchy and attractive so that customers would\r\nwant to buy them all off.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">We can add your logo and marking on\r\nthe custom CBD boxes to make them look attractive. Logos, photos, and patterns\r\ncan be printed on them, as per your demand. There is no limit. So you can get\r\nall creative.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">Make your business more appealing by\r\nmaking an impact with our custom CBD boxes!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Advertise your cannabis\r\nbusiness with custom boxes:<o:p></o:p></span>