r\ndamage during transit. Because the packaging would have been packed well. Going\r\nfor rigid boxes will give you more security and make sure that your products\r\nare safe!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Now we are going to explain the ways you can use our rigid\r\nboxes with ease!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">How to Use Rigid Boxes For Shipping Products?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">You can use rigid boxes as a form or packaging option for a\r\nnumber of different products such as food, wine, liquid medication, various\r\npapers, and other items. We also offer </span><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/custom-printed-boxes\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">custom printed boxes</span></a><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"> which can be customized according to\r\nyour requirements. For example, you can go ahead and make a sturdy customized\r\nbox for your electronic products if you want to keep them secure while they are\r\nin transit.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">There are many other ways you can use our rigid boxes. For\r\nexample, if you are using the boxes to ship any liquids, then they should be\r\nclosed with a plastic or shrink-wrap in order to keep them dry. Another tip\r\nthat will keep your items safe is to go for double-boxing. This means that you\r\nshould place one set of products inside a box and then put another box on top\r\nof it.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><br></span></