Custom rigid boxes are customizable rigid cardboard boxes,\r\nwhich can be tailor-made to your requirements on a number of different levels.\r\nWe have a team of designers who will go through your specifications to make\r\nsure that they can provide you with the right box.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">What are the advantages of using custom rigid boxes?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Custom rigid boxes are eco-friendly and durable as well so\r\nthat they can be used to ship your goods in more secure ways than in a regular\r\nbox. They will make sure that your items would not get any damage during\r\ntransit!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">What is the difference between custom rigid boxes and other types of\r\npackaging?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">We offer custom-made boxes for shipping purposes, as well as\r\nfor any other purpose as well. In addition, we also provide different sizes and\r\nshapes of boxes. Our boxes are tailor-made of the appropriate material, which\r\nwill keep your items safe.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">What is the reference number for a custom rigid cardboard box?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">The number that we use for a customized box is the four-digit\r\nreference number. This means that if you want us to make a particular box, then\r\nyou can go ahead and give us a four-digit reference number.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '2022-03-31 21:57:21', '2022-05-14 01:38:58');
