test printing\r\ntechnology and best ink stocks. Our goal is to provide our clients with an\r\nexperience tailored specifically to their desires and preferences so their\r\nbrand can gain maximum exposure.<span style=\"color:#0E101A\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '2022-03-31 21:57:21', '2022-05-14 01:43:09'),
(10, 'Custom Printed Boxes', 'custom-printed-boxes', 'You can have custom printed boxes made to stand out from the rest. It will promote your brand or product. Business owners who wish to design a custom printed box will want to create a brand identity that complements their business. Our packaging services are tailored to meet your company\'s needs and specifications. Your brand identity is kept by choosing custom boxes. Get in touch with us now to get the best service for custom printed boxes.', '<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;color:#0E101A\">You can have custom printed boxes made to stand\r\nout from the rest. It will promote your brand or product. Business owners who\r\nwish to design a custom printed box will want to create a brand identity that\r\ncomplements their business. Our packaging services are tailored to meet your\r\ncompany\'s needs and specifications. Your brand identity is kept by choosing\r\ncustom boxes. Get in touch with us now to get the best service for custom\r\nprinted boxes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'custom-printed-boxes.png', '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \">Custom Printed Boxes<o:p></o:p></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Small businesses face tough economic conditions right now.\r\nStanding out from the competition with your packaging design can help you\r\nattract new customers. The use of a custom box is one way to achieve this and\r\nis something to consider. A custom packaging box stands out from the crowd.\r\nThey promote the brand or product. If a business wishes to design a custom cardboard\r\nbox, it will want to create a product or brand identity that matches its\r\nbusiness.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Having a custom-designed box can serve a wide range of\r\npurposes. You can count on CustomBoxesUs if you need custom packaging boxes for\r\na product you are selling that are both affordable and effective. Our boxes\r\nhave proven popular with businesses that want boxes with their design. The\r\nboxes we design, print, and package ourselves. Cardboard packaging contains\r\nexactly what your brand needs to shine. This gives you full control over your\r\nbrand\'s packaging. Order today!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Custom Printed Boxes & Manufacturing Service<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Creating custom printed boxes is a great idea. Packaging of\r\nthis type enables you to include marketing messages, inserts, and specifics.\r\nYour customers will scan the entire shelf in one motion. It is 100% more likely\r\nthat they will choose the custom-printed box. As kids, we all played with\r\nLegos. Building something is fun, but tearing it down is even better. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">The same goes for </span><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\">custom packaging boxes</span></a><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">. However, instead of creating something for play or display,\r\ncustom product boxes act as storage containers, shipping containers, or display\r\ncases. Apart from their cost-effectiveness, companies choose custom shipping\r\nboxes for many reasons. In addition, custom shipping boxes catch customers\'\r\nattention while other forms of packaging do not. In addition, we offer\r\neconomical and efficient custom packaging services.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">A family business, we offer great customer care. Helping\r\ncustomers create the right packaging is one of our specialties. Printing and\r\nmanufacturing cardboard boxes are one of our specialties. We provide sizes,\r\npatterns, and designs to meet every need. Our boxes are also available with\r\ndifferent inserts.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">What to Expect With Custom Packaging Boxes?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Packaging is a mysterious thing. This is a container that\r\nholds all the goods that the consumer purchases. Moreover, it provides a\r\npreview of what the consumer can expect when they open the box. Hence, custom\r\nbox packaging allows you to showcase your brand. Your company will be proud of\r\nthe package. Whether you need a custom box printed or manufactured,\r\nCustomBoxesUs provides the best service.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">We are passionate about providing the right packaging for\r\nyour business. You can maintain your brand identity with custom-made cardboard\r\nboxes. The boxes are also ideal for marketing purposes. You can use the boxes\r\nboth as retail packaging and as displays. You can also reduce your landfill\r\nwaste by using them. They are made from environmentally friendly cardboard.\r\nThus, you can reuse, recycle, and repurpose them whenever you want.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Using our custom packaging boxes, professionals protect and\r\npresent their products with confidence. Our boxes provide superior protection\r\nto common packaging materials, whether they are being shipped or stored. Take a\r\nlook at the various styles, sizes, and materials of our boxes. Packaging is a\r\ncrucial aspect of any product, so it\'s best to go with quality packaging.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Brand Your Business With Custom Printed Boxes With Logos.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Are you an e-commerce retailer on a tight budget? Are you\r\nlooking for packaging options that will build brand recognition? Your goal is\r\nnot simply to ship orders but to make an impact. So what do you do? You can\r\ndesign your custom printed boxes with a logo using our custom boxes. The\r\nmessage of your brand can easily be communicated through stickers, labels, and\r\nfull-color printing. The top and bottom of the box can be printed with your\r\nbrand\'s logo.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Your package appears more professional this way. This will\r\nalso impress your customers. Logo printed boxes are a memorable and unique way\r\nto get your logo noticed. They are perfect for advertising, protection against\r\nproduct infringement, gifts, and retail packaging. With our custom printed\r\nboxes, we can make them in any size or color combination you need. Simply\r\nprovide us with your design and the colors you would like. After that, our\r\nexpert staff will handle everything.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Unique Boxes for Standing out In Business Packaging<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Packaging is essential when selling physical products. If you\r\ndon\'t, you may lose valuable customers. A failure to do so may prevent you from\r\nmeeting demand. Almost every small business faces this problem. Your product is\r\nfantastic. Unfortunately, packaging it incorrectly can make it look cheap.\r\nHowever, you are not alone. Therefore, wholesale custom printed boxes are your\r\nbest option.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">We at CustomBoxesUs provide businesses of all sizes and\r\nshapes with a range of packaging solutions. Choose from a variety of types of\r\ncustomized boxes available to you here. You can use these styles to\r\npromote your brand. They are ideal for trade show promotions, among other uses.\r\nYou can choose either square packaging or present-opening packaging, depending\r\non how you want to package your product. Reach out to us today to learn more\r\nabout what we can do for your business. <o:p></o:p></span></p>', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '2022-03-31 21:57:21', '2022-05-14 01:45:34'),
(11, 'Boxes Styles', 'boxes-styles', 'Your brand packaging needs can be met with a variety of box styles. Custom boxes can be designed based on the packaging style, the quantity, and the box size. Adding images, text, and even color will help them stand out. You can choose from a wide range of box types and sizes. With our instant quote system, you\'ll know exactly how much your final order will cost as you design.', '<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Your brand packaging needs can be met with a\r\nvariety of box styles. Custom boxes can be designed based on the packaging\r\nstyle, the quantity, and the box size. Adding images, text, and even color will\r\nhelp them stand out. You can choose from a wide range of box types and sizes.\r\nWith our instant quote system, you\'ll know exactly how much your final order\r\nwill cost as you design.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26);\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', 'boxes-styles.png', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '2022-03-31 21:57:21', '2022-05-14 12:48:49');

