y: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Are Macrons good for packaging?</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\">Macrons have gained a reputation for being highly durable, efficient, and\r\neffective packaging solutions. And we believe that our customization process\r\nwill be successful if you use our services to make your macron boxes unique and\r\neye-catching.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Is there any time I can order our products?</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\">We promote the fast and efficient transport of orders. We usually accept\r\nthem within a week or less. You can send us an email immediately and receive\r\nyour boxes on time.</span></p>', 'custom-macron-packaging-boxes', '1648896227_Custom Macron Boxes.jpg', '1648896227_Custom Macron Packaging Boxes.jpg', '1648896227_Custom Printed Macron Boxes.jpg', '1648896227_Custom Wholesale Macron Boxes.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'Custom Macron Packaging Boxes', 'Custom macron boxes to get your business started with your brands initial on them. We provide the best packaging solution to meet your needs.', 'Custom Macron Boxes', 'Custom Macron Packaging Boxes', 'Custom Printed Macron Boxes', 'Custom Wholesale Macron Boxes', NULL, 0, 4, 1, NULL, '2022-04-02 14:43:47', '2022-04-19 22:01:43'),
(28, 'Custom Pastry Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Printed Pastry Boxes</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Our pastry boxes are sure to meet your needs. There is a wide assortment of\r\nsizes and colors available at our store. Both windows and non-window boxes are\r\navailable. Your logo can be custom-printed on custom pastry boxes as well. Show\r\noff your company name to your customers as they leave your store with a custom\r\nbox bearing your company name. Hence, make your goods more valuable and\r\nrecognize your brand better.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">What do we offer at CustomBoxesUs?</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Custom pastry boxes are available in window boxes and non-window boxes. As\r\ncustomers leave your store, they can see your product through the window of the\r\nwindow box. Moreover, the number of boxes you get depends on . Please call us\r\nto discuss this offer with our customer service representatives.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom printed box sizes we can create:</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">-12\" x 12\" boxes<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">-8\" x 8\" boxes<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">-7.5\" x 7.5\" boxes<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">-6.5\" x 6