(29, 'Custom Bottle Boxes', NULL, '<h1><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Bottle Boxes </span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\">Whether you are shipping beverage containers of beer, cider, wine, or\r\nspirits in bulk, we can help. Our divider-style cardboard container boxes are\r\nideal for shipping beverage containers. We offer <a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/food-beverage-boxes\" target=\"_blank\">customized bottle boxes</a> in\r\nsizes from 3x4x12\" to 18x2.5x10.5\" and we also carry stock and custom\r\ndividers and corrugated packs to meet your individual needs.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Customization to make your boxes attractive:</span></h2><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\">We can make your boxes with full-color printing or have a simple colored\r\nlogo. We also offer custom-designed labels and tags for each of your\r\ncontainers. Hence, we can even make corrugated cards, plastic sleeves, and\r\nbubble wrap cases to cushion each container in transit.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Labeling:</span></h2><h2><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\">In addition to our dividers, we also offer a full line of beverage\r\ncontainers labeled for you. We print labels directly on the bottom of the cup\r\nor bottle itself so that you do not need to remove the label; saving you time\r\nand money on replacements.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">We package your product:</span></h2><h2><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\">We ship your product nationwide in 48 states plus international shipments\r\nworldwide. Moreover, we have a modern warehouse and distribution center where\r\nwe can quickly pack and ship orders. Additionally, we offer a variety of\r\npackaging options. We can use corrugated inserts, custom crates, and cardboard\r\nboxes to ship your products safely.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Dividers to make sure your products fit:</span></h2><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\">Our dividers are tailor-made of corrugated material, so they do not bend\r\neasily. We also use two or more dividers to make sure that your containers fit\r\nwell into any type of box. We also offer customized dividers and dividers with\r\na custom message or image. If you are shipping beverages, contact us for a\r\nquote today. We make sure that your product is well-protected from damage from\r\nthe time you ship it to the time it arrives at your customer\'s door.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Designs:</span></h2><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\">With the new color options, you have more options than just one color. Our\r\ngraphic designers are able to create a custom design for you. Find out more\r\nabout the full line of options available for your bottles and your box.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">For your custom bottle boxes, we can assist you with the perfect materials:</span></h3><h2><span style=\"color: r