\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">High-End Customization </span></h2><h3><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Consider using our high-end customized flower wraps for your clothing or\r\naccessory company. So, take a look at what our customers are saying about our\r\ngoods.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Customboxesus offers customizable bulk flower wraps with your logo, eyelets,\r\neyelets + ribbons, custom colors, and more choices. We are a Gift wrap Factory\r\nthat specializes in customized flower wraps and gift packing.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Click on any product picture to view the accompanying product page, which\r\nincludes sizes, colors, and other choices. Then, if needed, choose your size,\r\ncolor, and other choices. Also, to bring up the color name, hover your mouse\r\nover the color icon or touch on it if you\'re reading from a mobile device. On\r\nthe Cover Materials page, you can see our color charts. So, to view an\r\nexplanation of the choices, click on the Question Mark in circles. Then, to\r\nproceed with your purchase, add your goods to the shopping cart.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Our website functions similarly to any other online store, with the\r\nexception that our flower gift wraps are not ready-made, so in order to obtain\r\na quote, please add the necessary items to your cart, along with the options,\r\nand proceed to the checkout to be able to add logo application and shipping\r\nquotes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Our minimum purchase is just 40 wraps. So, you may mix and combine your\r\nwraps to experiment with different wrap designs.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Purchase in Bulk</span></h2><h3><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">As much as we would want to provide the lowest costs on the market, we are\r\nunable to match every customer expectation in this area since we design our\r\nwraps only using high-end eco-friendly materials. The main pricing issues are\r\nthe labor resources and the time necessary to hand-construct each wrap.\r\nCustomboxesus is the firm to go to if you want beautifully produced, high-\r\nCustom Flower Wraps that reflect your brand at its best. When you purchase\r\nin bulk, your order may be eligible for a tailored discount.</span></p>', 'custom-flower-wrap-packaging', '1649063033_Custom Flower Wraps.jpg', '1649063033_Custom Flower Wrap packaging.jpg', '1649063033_Custom Printed Flower Wraps.jpg', '1649063033_Custom Wholesale Flower Wraps.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Specifically designed for the export market, our Custom Flower Wrap packaging is water-resistant, strong, and heat-insulated available at Customboxesus.', 'Custom Flower Wrap', 'Custom Flower Wrap packaging', 'Custom Printed Flower Wraps', 'Custom Wholesale Flower Wraps', NULL, 0, 3, 1, NULL, '2022-04-04 13:03:53', '2022-04-17 01:04:02');
