(56, 'Custom Shoulder Rigid Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Give a luxury to your product using shoulder rigid boxes:</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Over the years we\'ve found that a rigid box can be an\r\nimportant accessory if you\'re giving a gift of jewelry. A luxurious shoulder\r\nrigid box will provide even a small piece with the protection it deserves. We\r\nat CustomBoxesUs have the ability to make your <a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/rigid-boxes\" target=\"_blank\">rigid boxes</a> into pure art! We at\r\nCustomBoxesUs understand that the presentation is just as important as the gift\r\nitself. So we have created a gift box to make the presentation of your gift\r\nexceptional!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">All of our rigid boxes are custom-made to fit your jewellery.\r\nOur boxes arrive flat for easy shipping and can be assembled by hand. We have a\r\nlarge library of images and logos to choose from or you can upload your own.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">The functionality of Shoulder Rigid Boxes:</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The shoulder rigid box determines the design of the\r\npackaging: 3 panels, 4 sides & flap. It is a mixture of <a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/rigid-boxes/custom-two-piece-rigid-boxes\" target=\"_blank\">two piece rigid boxes</a>.\r\nOne can be used to put a product inside and the other to put marketing\r\nmaterials on the outside of the flap one may be used to put some decoration\r\nlabels etc.<o:p></o:p