(78, 'Custom Gift Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Improving your gifts\' visual appeal by customizing your\r\ngift boxes:</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Your gift is a special thing. It deserves to be treated as\r\nsuch. That\'s why we\'re offering custom gift boxes! At CustomBoxesUs, you can\r\ncreate Custom Gift Boxes with your own personalized design, logo, and text\r\nprinted directly onto the box gift. You can also choose from our great range of\r\nvisuals that will surely impress anyone who opens them! No one likes to get\r\npresents in a plain brown box. In order to show that they\'re unique, make them\r\nsmile even before they\'ve opened the box by using custom gift boxes! <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">All of our boxes are tailor-made in the US. We offer free\r\ncustom design, free text, free proofs, and fast production times. At\r\nCustomBoxesUs, we are passionate about giving you the best custom gift boxes,\r\nand we will do everything to make your shopping experience with us a positive\r\none. Just let us know what you need, and we\'ll design what you want!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Customizing is a vast process:</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Our custom gift boxes are perfect for wrapping your\r\nprecious gifts since they must come in something that is unique and special. A\r\ncustom box is what you need when you have an item that needs to be custom-made.\r\nThe art of customizing your gift boxes is a vast process, and the perfect idea\r\nis what can really take your gift to the next level. When someone opens a gift\r\nbox with a custom design on it, they are mesmerized by its beauty. Another\r\nvital aspect of designing custom boxes for gifts is that it will make you stand\r\nout from others differentiating yourself from your competitors or from other\r\npeople. A Custom Gift Box offers so much more value than just wrapping paper\r\never will! And not only does it deliver more value. But we also offer free\r\ndesigns and free proofs.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Our Customization Process includes:</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Selecting Raw Material<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Sizes & Shapes<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Custom Visuals<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Selecting Raw Material:</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We make all of our boxes from eco-friendly material! Not\r\nonly they are recyclable, but they also are durable. Cardboard is the main\r\nmaterial that we use to make your gift box. The thickness of your gift box\r\ndepends on the size of the gift box. You can choose from different sizes,\r\nshapes, and colors. In the process of making our custom boxes, we only use\r\nrecycled material.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Size & Shape:</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"lin