(82, 'Jewelry gift Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"></p><h1><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); font-family: Helvetica;\">What\r\nOur Jewelry Gift Boxes Are All About </span><br></h1><p></p><h1 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Considering gift\r\nboxes for your jewelry gifts? With our vast selection of jewelry gift boxes,\r\nCustomboxesUS can help you find the packaging that best suits your needs. Each\r\nbox type can have cotton filler, velvet, or peach board inserts, and we sell\r\nthem in a variety of colors and sizes. We offer all sizes and styles of boxes\r\nto package <a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/jewelry-boxes/necklace-jewelry-packaging-boxes\" target=\"_blank\">necklaces</a>, <a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/jewelry-boxes/custom-bracelet-jewelry-packaging-boxes\" target=\"_blank\">bracelets</a>, <a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/jewelry-boxes/custom-bracelet-jewelry-packaging-boxes\" target=\"_blank\">earrings,</a> pendants, and bangles. There are\r\nmany options to choose from, including <a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/rigid-boxes\" target=\"_blank\">rigid boxes</a>, folding boxes, and elegant\r\nribbon boxes.  We have beautiful jewelry gift boxes that will help make\r\nyour jewelry gift stand out!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Here\r\nare some benefits and box construction details about our jewelry gift boxes:</span></h2><h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul type=