(84, 'Custom Popcorn Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Get\r\nCustom Popcorn Boxes at Best Wholesale Prices</span></h1><h1 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Popcorn Boxes</span></h1><h1 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The\r\ncinema and movie theaters would be incomplete without popcorn. Popcorn is at\r\nthe core of cinema experiences. This craze for popcorn is common among both\r\nadults and children. The best way to cheer up your group while watching a movie\r\nor the Super Bowl is with popcorn. So if you want to make your popcorn brand\r\nmore appealing, you should have custom popcorn boxes. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Our\r\n<a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/\" target=\"_blank\">custom packaging solutions</a> provide you with the best chance to attract\r\ncustomers. You can showcase your brand\'s potential by using popcorn packaging.\r\nWe will offer you some <a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/custom-printed-boxes\" target=\"_blank\">unique packaging designs</a> and ideas by immersing\r\nourselves in the packaging process! There are many different sizes and shapes\r\nthat you can choose from for your popcorn containers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We\r\noffer a wide range of materials and designs for our popcorn containers, so you\r\ncan select the packaging option that works best for you. With a few extra\r\nadd-ons, you can add some foiling to your font to make your packaging look\r\nluxurious! How cool is that? Request a quote today!<o: