(85, 'Custom Take Away Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Take Away\r\nBoxes</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Takeaway boxes are exactly what they sound like: a box\r\nwith a takeout spigot on top. They allow businesses to speed up the process of\r\nserving their customers by allowing them to make their own food, but they also\r\nallow consumers themselves to get food without having to leave the store.\r\nThey’re perfect for markets and other places where people might have to wait in\r\nline for service.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">At customboxesus we provide <a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/food-beverage-boxes\" target=\"_blank\">custom take away boxes</a> to the\r\nfood industry. This includes restaurants, cafes, corner markets and anywhere\r\nelse where people need to eat on the go or in a hurry.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Today, custom takeaway boxes are an integral part of the\r\nfood industry, and every restaurant has a unique custom takeaway box for their\r\nproducts. To carry the products inside, the boxes have to be sturdy and\r\ndurable. Protect the product inside the packaging from external forces and\r\ndamage. Don\'t leave the packaging behind.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Most brands and companies offer takeaway and home\r\ndelivery services. When a customer comes into your store, you can quickly pack\r\ncustom take away boxes. So the buyer doesn\'t have to spend valuable time eating\r\nwhile he is eating the food item. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Takeaway Boxes for your Brand at Wholesale\r\nPrices</span></h2><h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">If you are looking for a cost-effective solution for your\r\ncompany, buying takeaway boxes at wholesale is the best option. Nonetheless, if\r\nyou are on a tight budget, you should consider ordering bulk takeaway\r\npackaging. From CustomboxesUS, you can buy wholesale takeaway boxes at a\r\ndiscount. Further, wholesale custom take away boxes are less expensive than\r\nthose ordered in low-run quantities.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Take-away boxes that are eco-friendly</span></h2><h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We use biodegradable food-grade materials to manufacture\r\nour takeaway boxes. The materials we use are recyclable, which helps the\r\nenvironment. Customers who understand the importance of these materials and\r\nwant to improve the environment love these materials.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Various types of materials</span></h2><h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> There are many materials that can be used to make\r\ntakeaway boxes. Today, there are four main types of packaging available. The\r\nfour main types are cardboard, kraft paper, corrugated cardboard, and rigid\r\ncardboard. Below are their details:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The corrugated material is used where extra insulation and\r\n     protection are needed. For this reason, it has\r\n     flutes. There are 90 flutes per foot in our corrugated material. It\r\n     protects the inside of the product by providing a cushioning effect. <o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The solid material is the strongest and represents products\r\n     of the highest quality. Material that is the\r\n     most expensive but is widely used for products of high quality and high\r\n     cost. <o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">For manufacturing take-away packaging, cardboard is the most\r\n     commonly used material. Since it is the\r\n     cheapest material, it is the most popular.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Those who prefer eco-friendly environments use Craft, which\r\n     is 100% recyclable and biodegradable. Kraft is brown in\r\n     appearance but can be colored according to preference. <o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The above materials are available in various widths.\r\nBased on your budget and needs, you can choose any of them. A dozen points are\r\navailable (12pt, 14pt, 16pt, 18pt, 20pt, 22pt, 24pt). We can print custom take\r\naway boxes with the best quality on our state-of-the-art machines. Our printers\r\nuse food-safe and chemical-free inks, and we offer a variety of finishing\r\noptions you can pick based on what you need. E