oxes manufactured on demand by our\r\nreliable vendors with superior quality material and personalized messages\r\nprinted at our facility. These customized candy boxes are available in\r\nfull-color printing and delivered quickly to you as per your requirements.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Raw materials to consider for your candy boxes:</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Not all candy boxes are custom-made equal. That\'s why\r\nCustomBoxesUs uses only 100% recycled materials, including our famous heavy\r\npaperboard for their packaging. This is the same 100% recycled material as in\r\nbrown paper bags. It features high stiffness, durability, and a strong\r\ncorrugated feel thanks to its combination of recycled and virgin materials. So\r\nwhen you bring it home to share with friends and family, they\'ll know you chose\r\nan original. Cardboard is one of the most versatile materials today. Because\r\nit\'s so inexpensive and easy to work with. Cardboard has become a popular\r\nmedium for a packaging design for both consumer and commercial products.\r\nCardboard is tailormade from paper and ranges from super-thin packaging film to\r\nheavy-duty boxes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Design your boxes with eye-appealing visuals:</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">When decorating your custom candy boxes, consider the\r\nvisual appearance of your personal message. The front of a box is where you\'ll\r\nwant to showcase the greatest design and most impactful information, such as a\r\ngreeting message or holiday message. Choose a strong, meaningful graphic that\r\nstands out, while still being readable when viewed at an angle.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">To stand out from your competition and offer customers a\r\nunique product, choose a custom candy box with an eye-catching design that\r\nexpresses your personality. With more than half a million greeting cards, candy\r\nboxes have become one of the most popular promotional items for businesses and\r\ncharities around the world.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Add some catchy phrases to stand out:</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">In addition to striking images and text, your custom candy\r\nboxes will truly stand out when they are printed with high-quality ink. Use a\r\nlaser printer or inkjet printer to create crisp and vivid colors from our vinyl\r\ncandy boxes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Depending on your budget and tastes, you can choose from a\r\nlist of premium materials that make your gift pop. You may find a candy box\r\nmade of biodegradable, recycled paperboard or even aluminum foil. Our premium\r\npaperboard offers a more elegant look with a softer texture overall.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Advertise your brand with your candy packaging:</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We offer a number of shapes and sizes to customize and\r\nchoose from, from the most popular style to the unique and unusual. Consider\r\nyour candy selection when deciding on a design, as small candies look great in\r\ntall boxes. While chunky treats will look best when stored stacked in\r\ntop-loading boxes. If you\'re including larger or mixed candies, choose a wide\r\nbox for ease of filling, or a tall box for a variety of different-sized treats.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">With more than half a million greeting cards, candy boxes\r\nhave become one of the most popular promotional items for businesses and\r\ncharities around the world.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Eco-friendly Packaging Solutions:</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Paperboard is the most versatile packaging material on the\r\nmarket today. It offers a wide range of benefits, from the flexibility and\r\ndurability that makes it perfect for shipping and storage to its\r\ncost-effectiveness. What\'s more, because of its versatility, paperboard can be\r\nused in a variety of packaging applications. From gift boxes to toy boxes,\r\ncandy boxes are just one of the many applications we offer at CustomBoxesUs. We\r\noffer a variety of sizes and styles as well as premium materials that make your\r\ngifts memorable.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica;\">We offer attractive designs with eye-catching colors and\r\ngraphics printed on our custom cardboard candy boxes.</span><br></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Why Choose Us?</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We at CustomBoxesUs are focused on customer delight and\r\nalways providing top-notch services. We take pride in the fact that we deliver\r\nproducts with a wide range of specifications at the best prices. And we have\r\ngained immense confidence from customers through our strong business\r\npartnerships with reputed vendors. We offer a complete variety of customized\r\ncandy boxes at cheap rates. Our production is converted into a useful product\r\nthat meets the demands of customers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Being a one-stop shop for all your packaging needs, we also\r\noffer custom boxes in other shapes and sizes as per clients\' requirements. We\r\nare most prominent among our competitors because we provide better packing and\r\ndesign for customized cardboard candy boxes. Moreover, we provide customization\r\nof materials, sizes, shapes, and designs of the boxes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">FAQs</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">What are candy boxes?</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Candy boxes are containers that hold candy of various\r\nshapes and sizes. Even though candy boxes can be used for many different\r\npurposes, their most common use is to hold sweets for distribution at events\r\nand celebrations. Candy boxes are a fun way to add some flair to your party\r\nfavors and gifts.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">What are the benefits of using custom candy boxes?</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Candy boxes come in an endless arra